            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新鋼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2032:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2032\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2032-TW</a>)20日09:39上漲1.5元，股價漲停報16.9元，委買2,090張，成交1,760張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為不銹鋼板、捲裁切。不銹鋼板表面處理。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新鋼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2032:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2032\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2032-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲0.65%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.32%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-128 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-118 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-10 張</li> <li>融資增減：+18 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
